Domain Analysis for Space Invaders:

Constants:
-image of MTS
-image of invaders
-image of tank
-image of bullets

-speed of invaders
-speed of tank
-speed of bullets
-rate at which invaders appear on screen

Variables:
-y position of tank
-list of active bullets, and their x and y
-list of active invaders, and their x and y

World functions needed:
-on tick—progress 
-on key—have tank respond to left, right; create bullets with space
-render—show everything on the screen at one time
-stop-when—end game when an invader reaches the bottom of the screen
